<TEXT>
<P>
"We have a lot to do together in the fields of in-depth food
processing, farming technology, breeding improvements, and hi-tech
research," he said, and added that he will discuss opening up new
areas of co-operation with his American counterpart when he visits
the US with President Jiang.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, he added, a multi-level Sino-US cooperation in
agricultural area will help more US products accede into Chinese
market.
</P>
<P>
"There is a huge potential for Sino-US cooperation in the field
of agricultural products, and we are fully confident about the
future of food co-operation between the two countries," Zhou
said.  
</P>
