<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, October 19 (Xinhua) -- Prime Minister Inder Kumar
Gujral will begin a three-nation tour to Germany, France and the
United Kingdom on Tuesday to give a fresh boost to India's
political and economic relations with these countries, Press Trust
of India (PTI) said today.
