<HEADLINE> China's Largest Software Park Starts Operation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHENYANG, October 19 (Xinhua) -- China's largest software park
has become operational at the Shenyang New and High-Technology
Development Zone recently.
</P>
<P>
This heralds the beginning of the age of mass production in
China's software industry, said an official with the software park
which was attached to the Northeast China University.
</P>
<P>
