<HEADLINE> Lan Shizhang Breaks World Jerk Record </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
SHANGHAI, October 19 (Xinhua) -- Lan Shizhang of Guangxi
lifted 162.5 kilograms to break the world jerk record of the
men's 54kg category in the weightlifting competition of the
National Games here on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The previous record of 160kg was set by Halil Mutlu of
Turkey in the World Weightlifting Championships in Istanbul on
November 18, 1994. 
