Saturday as he attempted an unprecedented sixth successive amateur
world title in the World Amateur Boxing Championships.
</P>
<P>
Savon beat Sweden's Kwamena Turkson 4-2 after pulling out two
points in the last 40 seconds of their preliminary round bout.
</P>
