Rzany 9-4.
</P>
<P>
Cuban Olympic flyweight champion Maikro Romero, who has
downgraded to his preferred light-flyweight division, cracked
France's Mimount Chent 11-0.
</P>
<P>
Romanian light-flyweight Marian Velicu started a successful
first round, beating Mongolian Byambabayar Atarbayar 14-6. 
