<HEADLINE> Norman, Kucera Move into Ostrava Tennis Final </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PRAGUE, October 18 (Xinhua) -- Karol Kucera of Slovakia and
Magnus Norman advanced into the final of the ATP tennis tournament
in Ostrava, Czech Republic on Saturday.
</P>
